title: Fan Van at Madison Square Garden
text:
Fan Van at Madison Square Garden Where 
5:00 p.m. Friday, Oct. 16, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports COME SEE THE WFAN FAN VAN CREW OUTSIDE OF MADISON SQUARE GARDEN THIS FRIDAY AFTER WORK. WE’LL BE PATROLLING THE GROUNDS ON 31ST STREET BETWEEN 7TH AND 8TH AVENUE FROM 5 TO 7 PM BEFORE THE KNICKS PRESEASON GAME TIPS OFF, SO STOP BY AND ANSWER OUR KNICKS TRIVIA FOR A CHANCE TO WIN A COPY OF NBA 2K16 WHILE SUPPLIES LAST… NBA 2K16 FEATURES AN ALL NEW CAREER MODE WRITTEN AND DIRECTED BY CINEMA LEGEND SPIKE LEE. IT’S ALL FROM YOUR FLAGSHIP STATION FOR NEW YORK SPORTS, THE FAN… SPORTS RADIO 66 AND 101-9FM, WFAN AND WFAN-FM… NEW YORK.
